page.title: 11RANSKILL YOUTH CLUB
page.content: Our youth club is boring because nothing ever happens.I think the best thing was when a load of people barged in and took some of us outside to get punished!Ithink the other leaders were better because they brought things like inflatables and swing balls E.T.C. About thirty people came to the old one but now only about eighteen people come.Most people are just about always getting banned.At the senior youth club which is held at the church rooms is better but nobody goes.We all have to pay ten pence to get in and fifty pence for membership cards.Junior youthclub starts at 6.30pm on Tuesday.It is held in the school hall and Mr Thorpe's classroom.
